Comment: I feel like the difficulty level of this puzzle is just right. A nice thing about it is that it's solvable in low-level languages like C. I enjoyed solving this and am happy to approve it.

✅ Approved the contribution.
Comment: I solved this problem using Dart, and it was simple yet enjoyable. I really like problems like this that pop up every now and then because they give me the motivation to keep thinking and solving challenges. These kinds of simple problems are a great way to stay engaged and keep improving my problem solving skills.

Not all programming languages available on CodinGame can handle abitrarily large numbers like Python. Please limit n to 20 or below.

Please revise Constraints section, Test 3 and Validator 3 accordingly.

Thanks.

I think calculating factorial using caching/ storing the prior ones in an array would easily be enough for higher values too, yet since clash is supposed to be completed fast, I think it'll be in best interest to be updated.
